Risks
A space could be double booked.
A booking request may not update correctly after approval or cancelation
Users may be able to approve or edit bookings they do not own.
Unavailable dates may still appear selectable.
Invalid dates or prices may be accepted.

Assumptions
A booking is for one night only unless dates say otherwise
Only signed-in users can create spaces or request bookings.
Only the space owner can approve or deny requests.
Once a booking is confirmed, that night should no longer be available.
